    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "treatments and therapy... i've tried everything. doctors, meds, all of it. nothing actually stops it, it just dulls the edges for a few hours before it comes back even worse. it feels like a cycle that just never ends. sometimes i look at people who can just... exist without this constant agony, and i just feel so much envy. it feels so unfair that this is my reality every single day.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
