      "content": "The pain you describe is an incredibly heavy burden, and it makes complete sense that you feel exhausted from fighting a battle that no one else seems to understand. It is truly unfair that you feel so powerless and jealous of those who haven't to endure this constant agony, and your frustration is completely valid. Please know that while the cycle feels endless, there is a profound strength in simply enduring another day, and you deserve to be heard and helped with compassion.",
